data.description: Nestled in Capitol Hill, this charming 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath home boasts a thoughtfully designed and reconfigured kitchen, sure to delight any chef. The open-concept living area features a cozy wood-burning fireplace, perfect for those chilly evenings. Step out to a relaxing outdoor oasis with a quaint brick patio, ideal for al fresco dining and entertaining. During recent renovations, an extra half bath was added, enhancing the home's convenience and functionality. With its prime location, you'll find yourself just a short stroll away from Eastern Market and the vibrant Navy Yard, offering an array of dining, shopping, and entertainment options. For commuters, easy access to the nearby 295 highway ensures quick and convenient travel to both Virginia and Maryland. Experience the quintessential Capitol Hill lifestyle in this delightful home that combines style, functionality, and an unbeatable location. Don't miss your chance to call this gem your own!
